Name: Lead response time
Description: The time it took the current owner to perform a qualifying action on the contact. Qualifying actions include sending an email, calling, using chat, recording a meeting outcome, or marking a task as in progress or completed.

Name: Member has accessed private content
Description: 1 if a member has accessed any private content, 0 or null if not

Name: Registered member
Description: Whether or not a contact is registered

Name: IP Timezone
Description: The timezone reported by a contact's IP address. This is automatically set by HubSpot and can be used for segmentation and reporting.

Name: IP City
Description: The city reported by a contact's IP address. This is automatically set by HubSpot and can be used for segmentation and reporting.

Name: IP Country
Description: The country reported by a contact's IP address. This is automatically set by HubSpot and can be used for segmentation and reporting.

Name: IP Country Code
Description: The country code reported by a contact's IP address. This is automatically set by HubSpot and can be used for segmentation and reporting.

Name: IP State/Region
Description: The state or region reported by a contact's IP address. This is automatically set by HubSpot and can be used for segmentation and reporting.

Name: IP State Code/Region Code
Description: The state code or region code reported by a contact's IP address. This is automatically set by HubSpot and can be used for segmentation and reporting.

Name: Number of Form Submissions
Description: The number of forms this contact has submitted

Name: Number of Unique Forms Submitted
Description: The number of different forms this contact has submitted

Name: Recent Conversion Date
Description: The date this contact last submitted a form

Name: Recent Conversion
Description: The last form this contact submitted

Name: Close Date
Description: Date the  contact  became  a  customer. Set automatically when a deal or opportunity is marked as closed-won. It can also be set manually or programmatically.

Name: Days To Close
Description: Count of days elapsed between creation and being closed as a customer. Set automatically.

Name: First Deal Created Date
Description: Date first deal was created for contact. Set automatically.

Name: Buying Role
Description: Role the contact plays during the sales process. Contacts can have multiple roles, and can share roles with others.
Options: Blocker (BLOCKER) [READ-ONLY]; Budget Holder (BUDGET_HOLDER) [READ-ONLY]; Champion (CHAMPION) [READ-ONLY]; Decision Maker (DECISION_MAKER) [READ-ONLY]; End User (END_USER) [READ-ONLY]; Executive Sponsor (EXECUTIVE_SPONSOR) [READ-ONLY]; Influencer (INFLUENCER) [READ-ONLY]; Legal & Compliance (LEGAL_AND_COMPLIANCE) [READ-ONLY]; Other (OTHER) [READ-ONLY]

Name: Number of Associated Deals
Description: Count of deals associated with this contact. Set automatically by HubSpot.

Name: Recent Deal Amount
Description: Amount of last closed won deal associated with a contact. Set automatically.

Name: Recent Deal Close Date
Description: Date last deal associated with contact was closed-won. Set automatically.

Name: Total Revenue
Description: Sum of all closed-won deal revenue associated with the contact. Set automatically.

Name: Invalid email address
Description: The email address associated with this contact is invalid.
Options: True (true); False (false)

Name: Marketing emails bounced
Description: The number of marketing emails that bounced for the current email address. This is automatically set by HubSpot.

Name: Marketing emails clicked
Description: The number of marketing emails which have had link clicks for the current email address. This is automatically set by HubSpot.

Name: Email address quarantine reason
Description: The reason why the email address has been quarantined.
Options: Suspension Remediation (SUSPENSION_REMEDIATION) [READ-ONLY]; Blocklist Remediation (BLOCKLIST_REMEDIATION) [READ-ONLY]; Trust & Safety Remediation (TRUST_SAFETY_REMEDIATION) [READ-ONLY]

Name: Marketing emails delivered
Description: The number of marketing emails delivered for the current email address. This is automatically set by HubSpot.

Name: First marketing email click date
Description: The date of the earliest link click for any marketing email to the current email address. This is automatically set by HubSpot.

Name: First marketing email open date
Description: The date of the earliest open for any marketing email to the current email address. This is automatically set by HubSpot.

Name: First marketing email reply date
Description: The date of the earliest reply for any marketing email to the current email address. This is automatically set by HubSpot.

Name: First marketing email send date
Description: The date of the earliest delivery for any marketing email to the current email address. This is automatically set by HubSpot.

Name: Email hard bounce reason
Description: The issue that caused a contact to hard bounce from your emails. If this is an error or a temporary issue, you can unbounce this contact from the contact record.
Options: Content (CONTENT) [READ-ONLY]; Mailbox full (MAILBOX_FULL) [READ-ONLY]; Other (OTHER) [READ-ONLY]; Policy (POLICY) [READ-ONLY]; Spam (SPAM) [READ-ONLY]; Unknown user (UNKNOWN_USER) [READ-ONLY]

Name: Last marketing email click date
Description: The date of the most recent link click for any marketing email to the current email address. This is automatically set by HubSpot.

Name: Last marketing email name
Description: The name of the last marketing email sent to the current email address. This is automatically set by HubSpot.

Name: Last marketing email open date
Description: The date of the most recent open for any marketing email to the current email address. This is automatically set by HubSpot.

Name: Last marketing email reply date
Description: The date of the latest reply for any marketing email to the current email address. This is automatically set by HubSpot.

Name: Last marketing email send date
Description: The date of the most recent delivery for any marketing email to the current email address. This is automatically set by HubSpot.

Name: Marketing emails opened
Description: The number of marketing emails opened for the current email address. This is automatically set by HubSpot.

Name: Unsubscribed from all email
Description: Indicates that the current email address has opted out of all email.
Options: True (true); False (false)

Name: Opted out of email: One to One
Description: Indicates that the current email address has opted out of this email type.
Options: Yes (true); No (false)

Name: Opted out of email: Marketing Information
Description: Indicates that the current email address has opted out of this email type.
Options: Yes (true); No (false)

Name: Email Address Quarantined
Description: Indicates that the current email address has been quarantined for anti-abuse reasons and any marketing email sends to it will be blocked. This is automatically set by HubSpot.
Options: True (true); False (false)

Name: Email address automated quarantine reason
Description: The automated reason why the email address has been quarantined.
Options: Suspicious List Import (ON_LIST_IMPORT) [READ-ONLY]; High Hard Bounce Rate (HIGH_HARD_BOUNCE_RATE) [READ-ONLY]; Multiple Cancelled Campaigns (MULTIPLE_CANCELLED_CAMPAIGNS) [READ-ONLY]; Suspicious Form Activity (FORM_ABUSE) [READ-ONLY]; Recipient Complaint (RECIPIENT_COMPLAINT) [READ-ONLY]; Suspension Remediation (SUSPENSION_REMEDIATION) [READ-ONLY]; Blocklist Remediation (BLOCKLIST_REMEDIATION) [READ-ONLY]; Trust & Safety Remediation (TRUST_SAFETY_REMEDIATION) [READ-ONLY]; Other (OTHER) [READ-ONLY]; Undeliverable Email Address (UNDELIVERABLE_ADDRESS) [READ-ONLY]; Microsoft Undeliverable - Microsoft reports that address is inactive (MICROSOFT_UNDELIVERABLE)

Name: Marketing emails replied
Description: The number of marketing emails replied to by the current email address. This is automatically set by HubSpot.

Name: Sends Since Last Engagement
Description: The number of marketing emails that have been sent to the current email address since the last engagement (open or link click). This is automatically set by HubSpot.

Name: Marketing email confirmation status
Description: The status of a contact's eligibility to receive marketing email. This is automatically set by HubSpot.
Options: Confirmed; Confirmation Pending; Confirmation Email Sent; User clicked confirmation; HubSpot Rep. marked confirmed; Customer marked confirmed; Confirmed from previous behavior; Confirmed due to form

Name: Enriched Email Bounce Detected
Description: Bounce Detected attribute is populated when Hubspot & it’s partners identify the email may not be deliverable or is no longer valid for that contact.
Options: Yes (true); No (false)

Name: Legal basis for processing contact's data
Description: Legal basis for processing contact's data; 'Not applicable' will exempt the contact from GDPR protections
Options: Legitimate interest - Lead (Legitimate interest – prospect/lead) [READ-ONLY]; Legitimate interest - Customer (Legitimate interest – existing customer) [READ-ONLY]; Legitimate interest - Other (Legitimate interest - other) [READ-ONLY]; Performance of a contract [READ-ONLY]; Freely given consent from contact [READ-ONLY]; Not applicable [READ-ONLY]

Name: Quarantined Emails
Description: Lists all emails associated with this contact that have been quarantined, with a source and reason.

Name: Company size
Description: Contact's company size. Required for the Facebook Ads Integration. Automatically synced from the Lead Ads tool.

Name: Date of birth
Description: Contact's date of birth. Required for the Facebook Ads Integration. Automatically synced from the Lead Ads tool.

Name: Degree
Description: Contact's degree. Required for the Facebook Ads Integration. Automatically synced from the Lead Ads tool.

Name: Field of study
Description: Contact's field of study. Required for the Facebook Ads Integration. Automatically synced from the Lead Ads tool.

Name: Gender
Description: Contact's gender. Required for the Facebook Ads Integration. Automatically synced from the Lead Ads tool.

Name: Graduation date
Description: Contact's graduation date. Required for the Facebook Ads Integration. Automatically synced from the Lead Ads tool.

Name: Job function
Description: Contact's job function. Required for the Facebook Ads Integration. Automatically synced from the Lead Ads tool.

Name: Marital Status
Description: Contact's marital status. Required for the Facebook Ads Integration. Automatically synced from the Lead Ads tool.

Name: Military status
Description: Contact's military status. Required for the Facebook Ads Integration. Automatically synced from the Lead Ads tool.

Name: Relationship Status
Description: Contact's relationship status. Required for the Facebook Ads Integration. Automatically synced from the Lead Ads tool.

Name: School
Description: Contact's school. Required for the Facebook Ads Integration. Automatically synced from the Lead Ads tool.

Name: Seniority
Description: Contact's seniority. Required for the Facebook Ads Integration. Automatically synced from the Lead Ads tool.

Name: Start date
Description: Contact's start date. Required for the Facebook Ads Integration. Automatically synced from the Lead Ads tool.

Name: Work email
Description: Contact's work email. Required for the Facebook Ads Integration. Automatically synced from the Lead Ads tool.

Name: First Closed Order ID
Description: The id of the associated order that was first to be closed

Name: First Order Closed Date
Description: Date first order was closed. Set Automatically

Name: Recent Closed Order Date
Description: Date last order was closed. Set automatically.

Name: Contact unworked
Description: Contact  has  not  been  assigned  or  has  not  been  engaged  after  last  owner  assignment/re-assignment
Options: True (true); False (false)

Name: Lead Status
Description: The contact's sales, prospecting or outreach status
Options: New (NEW); Open (OPEN); In Progress (IN_PROGRESS); Open Deal (OPEN_DEAL); Unqualified (UNQUALIFIED); Attempted to Contact (ATTEMPTED_TO_CONTACT); Connected (CONNECTED); Bad Timing (BAD_TIMING)

Name: Owner assigned date
Description: The most recent timestamp of when an owner was assigned to this record. This value is set automatically by HubSpot.

Name: Contact owner
Description: The owner of a contact. This can be any HubSpot user or Salesforce integration user, and can be set manually or via Workflows.
Usages: Object requirement (1); Sales view (2); Properties v3 card (1)

Name: HubSpot Team
Description: The team of the owner of a contact.

Name: HubSpot Score
Description: The number that shows qualification of contacts to sales readiness. It can be set in HubSpot's Lead Scoring app.
